race.comment: HARA'S AVERY (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Dusty Jazz (21.91) in a Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Winning claims. SPEEDING FINE (1) ran below best last time finishing fifth (17.03) over 300m at Q Straight in a Mix 5. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Key runner on best form. UNTAMED VELOCITY (6) could manage only third at Rockhampton last time but turned heads when posting a blistering 23.68 over 407m at Rockhampton the start prior. Has the ability and can find winning form again. GOLDSTAR HARMONY (4) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.
